{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_017D7igncn66NfvThNNmycba","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→# Subdirectory Layout, Daemon-Side Extraction, and Poll Command\n     2→\n     3→**Date:** 2026-03-01\n     4→\n     5→## Overview\n     6→\n     7→Three related changes to Cloche:\n     8→\n     9→1. Move cloche project files into a `./cloche/` subdirectory of the host project, separating host-level files (CLAUDE.md, .git, build config) from agent-level files.\n    10→2. Replace the in-container git push mechanism with daemon-side result extraction using `docker cp` and host-side git operations (with worktrees for concurrency).\n    11→3. Add a `poll` command that blocks until a run reaches a terminal state or its container has been dead for >1 minute.\n    12→\n    13→## 1. Directory Layout\n    14→\n    15→### Host project (user's repo root)\n    16→\n    17→```\n    18→my-project/\n    19→├── .git/\n    20→├── .gitignore\n    21→├── .gitworktrees/         # Daemon-managed git worktrees (gitignored)\n    22→├── CLAUDE.md              # Host-level agent instructions\n    23→├── README.md\n    24→├── cloche/                # Everything cloche manages\n    25→│   ├── develop.cloche     # Workflow DSL file(s)\n    26→│   ├── Dockerfile\n    27→│   ├── CLAUDE.md          # Inner agent instructions\n    28→│   ├── .cloche/\n    29→│   │   ├── config\n    30→│   │   ├── prompts/\n    31→│   │   │   ├── implement.md\n    32→│   │   │   └── fix.md\n    33→│   │   ├── <run-id>/      # Per-run output (gitignored)\n    34→│   │   │   ├── prompt.txt\n    35→│   │   │   └── output/\n    36→│   │   └── ...\n    37→│   └── <source files>     # Project code the agent works on\n    38→└── <host-level files>\n    39→```\n    40→\n    41→### Inside the container\n    42→\n    43→```\n    44→/workspace/                # = contents of host's ./cloche/\n    45→├── develop.cloche\n    46→├── Dockerfile\n    47→├── CLAUDE.md\n    48→├── .cloche/\n    49→│   ├── config\n    50→│   ├── prompts/"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01AzU8HeMxKGnzFPbbezeUQh","session_id":"b83aa53c-b539-403e-957d-d27f065bd09c","uuid":"98bef03e-8dd6-4ddc-9aa3-cdf06d4f9fbf"}
